9 An Act relating to elections; amending 26 O.S. 2021,
Section 14-137, as amended by Section 1, Chapter 78,
10 O.S.L. 2024 (26 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 14-137),
which relates to definitions used in the Uniform
11 Military and Overseas Voters Act; modifying the
definition of covered voter to include an intent to
12 return and clarifying they were a bona fide resident
of Oklahoma; limiting voting for persons born outside
13 of Oklahoma and have never been a bona fide resident;
and providing an effective date.
14
