3 10. "United States", used in the territorial sense, means the
4 several states, the District of Columbia, Puerto Rico, the United
5 States Virgin Islands, and any territory or insular possession
6 subject to the jurisdiction of the United States.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
